:"015bda87d3b4cf7e610782f328eed4051a53a018","tid":2041303,"uid":232077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:18:02.000Z","msg":"條件係一定要有永久身份證，香港出世（雙親係香港出世亦可）同在中國內地冇任何物業<br />\n咁樣可以洗走一堆非真香港人如藍絲新移民走埋過去"},{"pid":"183270ba85ac272f41fc642204efc27f11ebbb6e","tid":2041303,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc696189737c46e1b9d734b24d40944e3e1ee317","tid":2041303,"uid":55321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44e8706fff9a6d0f5a74559306256496424e491e","tid":2041303,"uid":61589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"150同埋專材計劃蝗表示 : 今鋪fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:11:44.000Z","msg":"呢班最可恥 又食又拎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:18:12.000Z","msg":"仲有好多後門<br />\n入境處咁奶共,中意點批身份證俾蝗都得<br />\n大把共官同共諜會用香港身份證玩滲透<br />\n<br />\n孟晚舟都可以無喇喇有香港身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>三國圍繞孟晚舟周旋之際，香港未必可以獨善其身。《香港01》翻查公司註冊紀錄，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現孟晚舟持中國護照之餘，亦有香港身份證，無綫新聞更報道她是香港永久居民</span>。資料亦顯示，孟晚舟報住大角嘴豪宅維港灣一個由華為持有的高層單位。她目前擔任三間本港註冊的公司董事，包括「華為技術投資有限公司」、「香港華為國際有限公司」及「華盈管理有限公司」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然中國外交部和駐溫哥華領事館已有行動，但事件涉及港人，亦有不少跡象顯示事件可能與香港有關，惟至今未見特區政府採取行動。<span style=\"color: red;\">《香港01》昨日（7日）曾查詢保安局回應但不果，局方僅指不是由保安局回覆，沒有加以解釋。<br />\n<br />\n入境事務處（入境處）表示不評論個別個案</span>，強調在外香港居民如需協助，可致電入境處「協助在外香港居民小組」24小時求助熱線，電話為(852) 1868。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦則表示，對事件不作評論。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/268571/%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%8C%81%E6%B8%AF%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E8%AD%89-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E6%8B%92%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E4%B8%8D%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F268571%2F%25E5%25AD%259F%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%2588%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%259C%259B&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=d8c7eea0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/268571/%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%8C%81%E6%B8%AF%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E8%AD%89-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E6%8B%92%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E4%B8%8D%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B</a>"},{"pid":"b210391a78bda196f9fad2c91fb769ab1b45034d","tid":2041303,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"唔應該<br />\n太撚多藍絲"},{"pid":"509558639d74b4380223a16f2b27a7668200f4fa","tid":2041303,"uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:23:26.000Z","msg":"所有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹太大<br />\n益撚晒啲間諜"},{"pid":"d47976703c3335681b5b86802bd31106fefd4c87","tid":2041303,"uid":311119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95359f8dec250548f2daf21e78a83d60ecb7c5a","tid":2041303,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"So sad to see Hong Kong, the most efficient, fair &amp; free trading rule of law jurisdiction in the world being undermined. What a waste. We should offer all HK citizens UK residence, and take on board as much of the Hong Kong ethic as we can, for similar freedoms and dynamism.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarcusFysh/status/1265759943443066880?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarcusFysh%2Fstatus%2F1265759943443066880%3Fs%3D19&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=1fcf710f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarcusFysh%2Fstatus%2F1265759943443066880%3Fs%3D19&h=1684cd74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarcusFysh/status/1265759943443066880?s=19</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"咁樣同香港日日百五個有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家我地都鬧9啲大陸人日日落黎<br />\n點解會覺得啲英國人想我地啲無BNO嘅過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到做二等公民 不了不了 <br />\n港人自決！"}]}